        <div id="download">
          <h3>Downloads</h3>
          <h4>System Requirements</h4>
          <p>
            Artemis needs a recent version of Java v1.5 or higher.
          </p>
          <p>
            For installation instructions please see the <a href=
            "ftp://ftp.sanger.ac.uk/pub4/resources/software/artemis/artemis.pdf">Artemis manual</a>.
          </p>
          <h4>Download current version</h4>
          <p>
            The latest release of Artemis is available for Unix, Macintosh and Windows. It can also be launched with Java Web
            Start.
          </p>
          <h4>Java Web Start</h4>
          <ul>
            <li class="launch">
              <a href="/resources/software/artemis/java/artemis.jnlp"><img alt="Launch Artemis" src="/i/blank.gif" /></a> Artemis
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="http://java.sun.com/javase/technologies/desktop/javawebstart/">Get Java Web Start</a>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <h4>FTP Download</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <a href="ftp://ftp.sanger.ac.uk/pub4/resources/software/artemis/artemis.tar.gz">Artemis for UNIX</a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="ftp://ftp.sanger.ac.uk/pub4/resources/software/artemis/artemis.dmg.gz">Artemis for MacOSX</a>
              <sup><a href="#note_3">[3]</a></sup>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="ftp://ftp.sanger.ac.uk/pub4/resources/software/artemis/artemis.jar">Artemis for Windows</a> <sup><a href=
